# Docker-first workflow (required)

This repo is Docker-first. Assume **the host may not have Node installed**.

- Run all npm/next commands **inside the `web` service container**.
- Prefer `make` targets when available.

## Common commands

- Start dev server: `make up`
- Rebuild + restart: `make rebuild`
- Open a shell: `make sh`
- Lint: `make lint`
- Production build: `make build`

## Installing dependencies

- Install/update deps: `docker compose run --rm web npm install`
- For a clean install: `make nuke`

## Notes

- `node_modules` is installed into the repo (bind mount) so the editor can resolve imports.
- Avoid suggesting `npm install` on the host unless explicitly asked.

